# UI Locator Repair Playground

This repository is intentionally designed to test an agent's ability to
repair UI tests after UI changes.

## Scenario

A UI test fails because a locator used in Playwright tests is no longer valid
after HTML changes.

The agent is expected to:
1. Analyze the failing test
2. Identify what changed in the HTML
3. Update the locator
4. Open a MR with the fix

## Stack
- Playwright
- Plain HTML (no framework)

## Usage

```bash
npm install
npm run install:browsers
npm run start
npm test
